{"tid":857830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前FCC主席、港大新聞研究中心總監 Keith Richburg：「香港之死」終來臨","createTime":"2018-10-11T10:57:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-11T12:08:06.000Z","uid":48083,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"9a2f7c336d118911993e9a4870d51fe055b7d314","tid":857830,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T10:57:38.000Z","msg":"特區政府引用社團條例，禁止香港民族黨運作，之後外國記者會第一副主席馬凱工作簽證不獲續期，外界都認為是政府報復外國記者會邀請民族黨前召集人陳浩天演講。曾任香港外國記者會（FCC）主席、現任港大新聞及傳媒研究中心總監的瑞凱德（Keith Richburg）在網上撰文，標題開宗名義，指「用了一段時間，但香港之死終來臨（It took a while,but  'The Death of Hong Kong' has arrived）」。立場新聞獲瑞凱德授權全文轉載其文章。<br />\n<br />\n瑞凱德亦接受《立場新聞》專訪，指「現在香港是受北京控制（Hong Kong is now under Beijing' s thumb）」。外國記者寫了「冒犯」的文章，就會被驅逐。他又認為，「兩制愈來愈變得不可行，已漸漸變成一國」，這十分不幸「將會侵蝕香港的特別地位」，瑞凱德亦和《立場》分享他在香港這個自由城市，作為外國記者的經驗，請留意《立場》稍後報道。<br />\n<br />\n一個曾經偉大、自由的城市　開始崩壞<br />\n<br />\n瑞凱德在文章中，引用1995年財富雜誌封面著名的標題「香港之死（The Death of Hong Kong）」，指當年歷史學家預言香港回歸代表香港之死，可能是有先見之明或來得太早，但2018年這幾個月發生的事，似乎是一個轉捩點，標誌一個曾經偉大，開放而自由的城市開始崩壞（the demise of a once-great open and liberal city really began）。<br />\n<br />\n他解釋他所指的轉捩點，是今年7月保安局考慮回歸以後首次引用社團條例，禁止香港民族黨運作，到10月馬凱被拒絕續批工作簽證，是他記憶中首次香港透過不更新工作簽證，驅逐外國記者。<br />\n<br />\n未想過有一天香港會驅逐外國記者<br />\n<br />\n瑞凱德表示他在東亞地區做記者30年，曾在印尼蘇哈托軍事獨裁政權紀治期間，因為撰文指總統蘇哈托發動政變奪權，被印尼禁止入境兩年；他亦因為潛入當地訪問昂山素姬，被禁入緬甸20年，緬甸亦長年在軍事獨裁下，但他「從來沒有想像過，有一天香港會驅逐外國記者」（Never could I imagine that one day Hong Kong would be expelling a foreigh correspondent）。<br />\n<br />\n他憶述他1995年首次到香港設立《華盛頓郵報》分部，獲邀和當時的政府新聞處處長（編按：1995年政府新聞處處長為丘李賜恩）午餐，瑞凱德問對方申請記者證，新聞處處長只是笑一笑，稱香港不需要申請記者證：「我們有新聞自由（We have freedom of the press here）。」<br />\n<br />\n港府為「殺雞儆猴」<br />\n<br />\n瑞凱德表示，拒絕續批簽證一直都是中國政府的手法，今次港府明顯「借用」了中國的一套，作為「管控的手段」（means of control），但馬凱的情況實際上更惡劣，因為馬凱不是因為他寫的任何文章而被趕走，他的「罪行」似乎是他作為外國記者會執行主席，主持了一個「絕對合法的午餐會（perfectly legal luncheon talk）」。<br />\n<br />\n他相信港府的做法是為了「殺雞儆猴」，拒絕馬凱的工作簽證續期後，其他外國記者會明白政權的態度已改變，具批判性的報道不會被容忍，「最好聽從命令或執包袱離開（it' s best to toe the line or pack up and leave）」。他預期大部份外國記者不會離開，但在報道時會更小心謹慎，甚至因為擔心被驅逐而自我審查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/馬凱被逐-港大新聞研究中心總監-香港之死-終來臨/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%A6%AC%E5%87%B1%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%90-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%B8%BD%E7%9B%A3-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B9%8B%E6%AD%BB-%E7%B5%82%E4%BE%86%E8%87%A8%2F&d=%2FXhWzRbh9n3AG2teqPVqX9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=4731f56b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%A6%AC%E5%87%B1%E8%A2%AB%E9%80%90-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%A0%94%E7%A9%B6%E4%B8%AD%E5%BF%83%E7%B8%BD%E7%9B%A3-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%B9%8B%E6%AD%BB-%E7%B5%82%E4%BE%86%E8%87%A8%2F&h=8b61f279\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/馬凱被逐-港大新聞研究中心總監-香港之死-終來臨/</a>"},{"pid":"5a588cf2ff4dfcff668f303c18ea349bb533dd48","tid":857830,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> The city is dying"},{"pid":"a8778668a4f40cab33820fd0c9d623db1f7d0cb1","tid":857830,"uid":4942,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:02:46.000Z","msg":"他預期大部份外國記者不會離開，但在報道時會更小心謹慎，甚至因為擔心被驅逐而自我審查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aef320fd06208c3f0ff1e094e4878d3c20ad812","tid":857830,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:03:48.000Z","msg":"The dying city <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9642809fca4d324f66d2927edb628cc649ac378","tid":857830,"uid":142233,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"點解依班係香港做野既記者都咁撚離地，依4，5年香港政府做過既衰野有咩唔係歷年首次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8825ee27865641e58a3f56e88de3f275e47f6f","tid":857830,"uid":140538,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:07:55.000Z","msg":"但馬凱的情況實際上更惡劣，因為馬凱不是因為他寫的任何文章而被趕走，他的「罪行」似乎是他作為外國記者會執行主席，主持了一個「絕對合法的午餐會（perfectly legal luncheon talk）<br />\n<br />\n唔知班港共明唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c798f04a33a0479a7ec30f443bca4ca2eee621c","tid":857830,"uid":37375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5a588cf2ff4dfcff668f303c18ea349bb533dd48","tid":857830,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> The city is dying"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:27:14.000Z","msg":"is dead"},{"pid":"a9fcd9526fe253503c6a9c73b3f8cf61bb84b1fb","tid":857830,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:29:00.000Z","msg":"香港 死撚緊<br />\n外國記者係就係左膠, 但好撚團結<br />\n<br />\n你得罪一條友慘撚過批鬥"},{"pid":"aa908cd9b121d1dbde639affe6af2bb3b9815c1f","tid":857830,"uid":153239,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b9642809fca4d324f66d2927edb628cc649ac378","tid":857830,"uid":142233,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:05:45.000Z","msg":"點解依班係香港做野既記者都咁撚離地，依4，5年香港政府做過既衰野有咩唔係歷年首次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:33:18.000Z","msg":"挑<br />\n記者比人打出句聲就冇聲氣<br />\n根本班妓者都只係為逗份糧<br />\n<br />\n同d龜一撚樣<br />\n咩真相 咩正義 咩抱負 咩責任<br />\n通通都冇<br />\n<br />\n不如cut哂佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83f48709986d579040ad126670ab29e2aa935cd7","tid":857830,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:33:25.000Z","msg":"等睇港共繼續外交部式回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2c9bcc3a79365d281bd4b23ed3c51c60bb2f46","tid":857830,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:35:37.000Z","msg":"變新加坡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcdb43ffa011bf4a3189478c2831fc0ad898ef9b","tid":857830,"uid":87339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"83f48709986d579040ad126670ab29e2aa935cd7","tid":857830,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:33:25.000Z","msg":"等睇港共繼續外交部式回應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:36:12.000Z","msg":"新加坡冇新聞自由<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82fdadfd5e13d7db4b20bc623b39e37132e7d959","tid":857830,"uid":208722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:36:48.000Z","msg":"都死咗好多年，而家先如夢初醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c394c4fa65758b6427bc0320a026a3637c7f93","tid":857830,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:39:01.000Z","msg":"屌做咗咁多年都唔明問題唔係北京 係港府"},{"pid":"99b7b8c05b6ea4e8b9a9aafe61d33f3911c11b30","tid":857830,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:39:39.000Z","msg":"大蜀民國認為，問題的實質是，中國恐怖組織的香港代理人，侵犯了香港民族國家的主權。我們雖然維護言論自由的原則，但<span style=\"color: red;\">從未忘記抽象的原則只有通過具體的法律才能落實，而當今之世大多數法律和權利，是以民族國家為執行主體的</span>。香港民族的言論自由得不到保障，關鍵在於國際社會無法代替香港民族國家。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/liuzhongjing/status/1049982634196180992?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fliuzhongjing%2Fstatus%2F1049982634196180992%3Fs%3D21&d=%2FXhWzRbh9n3AG2teqPVqX9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=a8641c05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fliuzhongjing%2Fstatus%2F1049982634196180992%3Fs%3D21&h=5e7f4f7f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/liuzhongjing/status/1049982634196180992?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n講到好明，法治&mdash;&gt;港獨"},{"pid":"1c8ab4340067e88a71e38a7c1c9c22fff181d296","tid":857830,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T11:53:14.000Z","msg":"曾任香港外國記者會（FCC）主席、現任港大新聞及傳媒研究中心總監的瑞凱德（Keith Richburg）在網上撰文<br />\n<br />\n好快失業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1759ac27fa02070f067f8b339b3ec49c865fbb0","tid":857830,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T12:08:06.000Z","msg":"死亡"}]}